{"tid":2357355,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國間諜晶片惹疑慮　東芝攜手早稻田開發偵測工具","createTime":"2021-01-07T11:10:27.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T11:40:15.000Z","uid":75656,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"df0be645fd6bcc4993f765266983435897bff814","tid":2357355,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:10:27.000Z","msg":"《日經亞洲評論》報導，東芝（TOSHIBA）和早稻田大學（Waseda University）已合作開發出一個系統，能夠偵測所謂的「間諜晶片」，可望協助企業和政府機關抵禦日益增長的網路攻擊。<br />\n<br />\n由於這類偷偷被植入半導體或電路板中的間諜晶片難以用肉眼察覺，東芝和早稻田大學合作研發了一個名為「HTfinder」的工具，可用於判斷半導體內是否夾藏間諜晶片。東芝旗下東芝情報系統（TOSHIBA INFORMATION SYSTEMES）最近已推出相關檢驗與分析服務。<br />\n<br />\n《日經》指出，使用「HTfinder」進行檢測，需時約2周可得到結果；至於檢測與分析費用，預計為每項產品200萬日圓左右，但視硬體產品類型而定收費將會有差異。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20210107/7XLHBLKXVFG2FLLY7RUHRIHSTY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20210107%2F7XLHBLKXVFG2FLLY7RUHRIHSTY%2F&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z7%2FszHQdc4%2B4ddc640yZrNs%3D&h=bcbe6b88\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fproperty%2F20210107%2F7XLHBLKXVFG2FLLY7RUHRIHSTY%2F&h=2e730fbc\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/property/20210107/7XLHBLKXVFG2FLLY7RUHRIHSTY/</a><br />\n<br />\n日經:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://asia.nikkei.com/Business/Technology/Toshiba-s-detector-sniffs-out-spy-chips-lurking-in-hardware\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fasia.nikkei.com%2FBusiness%2FTechnology%2FToshiba-s-detector-sniffs-out-spy-chips-lurking-in-hardware&d=vTNdr7lgiRBdtcQZ4wg6z7%2FszHQdc4%2B4ddc640yZrNs%3D&h=1709a940\" target=\"_blank\">https://asia.nikkei.com/Business/Technology/Toshiba-s-detector-sniffs-out-spy-chips-lurking-in-hardware</a>"},{"pid":"2de3f308deee3d959c02234a43a2179c483066a7","tid":2357355,"uid":107927,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T11:11:50.000Z","msg":"東芝唔係被美的收購左？"},{"pid":"b77db24dfa72145daa3041454d00783b6d21358e","tid":2357355,"uid":7857